{"tid":364354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院少數黨領袖佩洛西轟裁決不公：以卑劣手段阻港人追求民主","createTime":"2017-08-18T10:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T11:03:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24d54bdb4534fda44c4153d64fc5493d18f6621a","tid":364354,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"美國國會眾議院少數黨領袖、民主黨眾議員佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）發表聲明，指「雙學三子」被改判入獄6至8個月的裁決是不公義，裁決也是中國違背「一國兩制」承諾的最新證據，更形容昨日是「民主黑暗的一天」（dark day for democracy）。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西在聲明中表明，三子被判監消息「撼動全球的良知（shock the conscience of the world）」。她認為法院的「過份（egregious）」決定，令致力爭取香港普選的雙學三子，未來5年都無法參與香港各級選舉，是以「不公義和卑劣(unjust and underhanded attempt)」的手段阻止香港人對民主的追求。<br />\n她續指，自雨傘運動發生後，中國加速對人權鎮壓，三子被判刑同時是中國違背「一國兩制」承諾的最新證據。但北京政府對港人自由的破壞越猛烈，勢必令民主運動更加壯大，「任何壓迫及威嚇永遠不能打擊人民追求普選、自由及公義的宏願」。<br />\n聲明又指，裁決不單侵犯香港原有的自由及民主價值，應受到國際社會聯合譴責。她重申美國在道德上有責任就不公義事件發聲，若因為與中方有貿易往來考慮，在今次事件選擇噤聲，以後就會喪失道德力量去談論全球人權狀況。她又為三子以及追尋更有希望、有更自由未來的香港人送上支持。"},{"pid":"62fa485c6a08c413d5366a79589932b5aee51efa","tid":364354,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"佩洛西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩譯名嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645a4c925235ffcac7fb5f8566ce669ac7fb1d8b","tid":364354,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"邊撚個<br />\n<br />\n聽都味聽過<br />\n<br />\n人起采你起采"},{"pid":"58f8f93cfe3045492666fdae065e08853e0df7b8","tid":364354,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"Pelosi假慈悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb666d3761c842f13158821d12f67a65b51c642","tid":364354,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:59:34.000Z","msg":"又係成頁都係block晒"},{"pid":"bd61d4402e7d11fe59add51eb503113cc6f34463","tid":364354,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7495205eb21be473aafad65262efdd0a8cd90745","tid":364354,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"少數黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aad81116216f25476e5211764b853281f869777","tid":364354,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少數黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地真係Minority Party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}